<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425975' id='t-425975'>we're going to take care of you
when you're old and senile.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='428801' id='t-428801'>No, just kidding.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:21
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='430118' id='t-430118'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='431142' id='t-431142'>No, really, we are going
to be the next generation,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='433861' id='t-433861'>the ones who will bring
