</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463145' id='t-463145'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465000' id='t-465000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468000' id='t-468000'>Thank you. Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
